msgstr "最小値は最大値より小さい値を設定してください。"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:980
msgid "Please enter a number."
msgstr "数値を入力してください。"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:985
#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/post-date-search-pro/edit.js:426
msgid "Please enter a date in the format \"YYYY-MM-DD\". (e.g. 2020-01-01)"
